txt.en: 'From the shadows of Moria came great trolls, and cloaked in the mists of the mountains on that dark winter's day, they set siege upon us at Azanulbizar.'
Many were the trolls slain during the Battle of Azanulbizar.
'Terrible were the trolls come out of Moria, but many more would fall that day!'
